  <note reference-line="4" id="0">
    <original>sādhu ṭhito sato bodhiṃ samajjheganti (sī. pī.), sādhu vatamhi satto bodhisamajjhagūti (syā. kaṃ.)</original>
    <type>no_match</type>
    <snippet> me sutaṃ – ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā uruvelāyaṃ viharati najjā nerañjarāya tīre ajapālanigrodhamūle paṭhamābhisambuddho. Atha kho bhagavato rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi – ‘‘mutto vatamhi tāya dukkarakārikāya. Sādhu mutto vatamhi tāya anatthasaṃhitāya dukkarakārikāya. Sādhu vatamhi mutto bodhiṃ samajjhaga’’nti </snippet>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="sī." source="sri lanka">sādhu ṭhito sato bodhiṃ samajjheganti</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="pī." source="pali text society">sādhu ṭhito sato bodhiṃ samajjheganti</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="syā." source="thai">sādhu vatamhi satto bodhisamajjhagūti</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="kaṃ." source="kam">sādhu vatamhi satto bodhisamajjhagūti</alternative>
    </alternatives>
  </note>
